    {"id":"product","type":"text","text":"## PRODUCT V1 (beside EMR) ✅\n- A · Missed-call & after-hours capture (wedge)\n- B · Speed-to-lead pipeline (clinic CRM)\n- C · Ad→patient attribution + dashboard (MOAT)\n- D/E · Rebooking + reactivation 🔵","x":-180,"y":-400,"width":320,"height":200,"color":"4"},
    {"id":"integration","type":"text","text":"## INTEGRATION 🔵\n- Own-the-funnel (leads in OUR CRM) ✅\n- EMR adapter layer (1 plugin / EMR)\n- Cliniko + Juvonno = open API ✅\n- Jane = JDP partner API + own-funnel\n- ⚠️ GCal can't create bookings","x":360,"y":-400,"width":320,"height":200,"color":"5"},
